171 A.3d 1254 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DERRICK M. MILLER, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER. STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF, v. ARTHUR L. THOMPSON, A/K/A NASHEED, DEFENDANT.

C-223 Sept.Term 2017

079425 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-4022/4055-12 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
